### Summary of Changes
1. **Idempotence on Upgrade**: Updated [bb007_migrate/migration.py](file:///home/forcewake/coding-agent-battles-init/runs/2026-06-22-bb-007-sqlite-migration-rollback/agents/agy/workspace/bb007_migrate/migration.py) to check the table info schema via `PRAGMA table_info(users)` before attempting to add the `email` column, avoiding failure on consecutive upgrade calls.
